    "ai_summary": "Visakhapatnam Steel Plant (RINL) is an integrated iron and steel manufacturing facility that processes imported coking coal and iron ore. Its main process steps include coking coal carbonization, iron ore sintering, hot metal production in blast furnaces, and conversion to liquid steel in Steel Melt Shops. The liquid steel is then continuously cast into blooms, which are hot-rolled into finished products like TMT rebar, wire rods, and structural sections.",
